title: Boat Inflate/Deflate
story: dungeo
description: Tests inflating and deflating the rubber boat

---

# Setup - go to Shore where the boat is
> gdt
[OK: contains "GDT"]

# Give ourselves the lamp
> tk brass lantern
[OK: contains "Taken"]

# Teleport to Shore (Frigid River region)
> ah Shore
[OK: contains "Shore"]

> ex
[OK: contains "Returning"]

# Turn on lamp for light
> turn on lantern
[OK: contains "on"]

# Verify we can see the boat (starts deflated as "pile of plastic")
> look
[OK: contains "plastic"]

# Boat starts deflated - examine it
> examine plastic
[OK: contains "valve"]

# Try to deflate when already deflated - should fail
> deflate boat
[OK: contains "already_deflated"]

# Try to inflate without pump - should fail
> inflate boat
[OK: contains "no_pump"]

# Get the pump via GDT
> gdt
[OK: contains "GDT"]

> tk hand pump
[OK: contains "Taken"]

> ex
[OK: contains "Returning"]

# Now inflate the boat with the pump in inventory
> inflate boat
[OK: contains "inflates"]

# Verify boat is now inflated - examine shows new description
> examine boat
[OK: contains "seaworthy"]

# isInflated should be true
> examine boat
[OK: contains "oars"]

# Try to inflate again - should fail
> inflate boat
[OK: contains "already_inflated"]

# Deflate the boat
> deflate boat
[OK: contains "deflates"]

# Verify it's back to pile of plastic
> look
[OK: contains "plastic"]

# Alternative syntax: "open valve" to deflate
> inflate boat
[OK: contains "inflates"]

> open valve
[OK: contains "deflates"]

# Alternative syntax: "pump boat" to inflate
> pump boat
[OK: contains "inflates"]

# Alternative syntax: "pump up boat"
> deflate boat
[OK: contains "deflates"]

> pump up boat
[OK: contains "inflates"]
